<P><H5><U><B>Overview</B></U></H5><P>
<p>The electronic Ligand Builder and Optimization Workbench (eLBOW) is the
primary tool for generating non-standard ligand restraints in Phenix.  In
addition to existing as a standalone program, it is also used internally by
the <a class="reference" href="ligandfit_gui.htm">LigandFit wizard</a> and <a class="reference" href="refine_gui.htm">phenix.ready_set</a> (integrated with the <tt class="docutils literal"><span class="pre">phenix.refine</span></tt> GUI).  In addition
to eLBOW, a separate standalone <a class="reference" href="reel.htm">graphical restraint editor</a> is
available for advanced customization of restraints and structures.</p>
